  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of a multi-barreled tank and face off against digital viruses! Navigate through the motherboard, battle powerful bosses, and unlock new zones. Keep an eye on the Upgrade Machine – it boosts your abilities every 1-10 seconds. Earn points from previous runs to enhance your upgrade potential and outsmart the bugs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697390/extras/0165a8995f057dda72ea1bc230c67ff6.poster.avif?t=1734593725\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697390/extras/0165a8995f057dda72ea1bc230c67ff6.webm?t=1734593725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697390/extras/0165a8995f057dda72ea1bc230c67ff6.mp4?t=1734593725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 21-Track Soundtrack by DOS - 88</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 25 Base Enemies + 5 Spawn Bosses</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 10 Main Bosses to conquer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unique Weapons & Upgrades</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Collectables: Player icons & mousepads</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697390/extras/07466ef461f5e9c82bccace9b6f7cc53.poster.avif?t=1734593725\" width=502 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697390/extras/07466ef461f5e9c82bccace9b6f7cc53.webm?t=1734593725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697390/extras/07466ef461f5e9c82bccace9b6f7cc53.mp4?t=1734593725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Dynamic Maps & Lighting </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Custom Probability Algorithm</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697390/extras/e9d8808d632cfb1a4086126d2915ed99.poster.avif?t=1734593725\" width=340 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697390/extras/e9d8808d632cfb1a4086126d2915ed99.webm?t=1734593725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697390/extras/e9d8808d632cfb1a4086126d2915ed99.mp4?t=1734593725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for chaos, strategy, and non-stop action!</p>",
